      "content": "@echo off\ntitle KayocktheOS\ncolor 0A\nset KAYOCK_ROOT=%~dp0\ncd /d \"%KAYOCK_ROOT%\"\n\necho Starting KayocktheOS...\necho.\n\nwhere python >nul 2>nul\nif %errorlevel%==0 (\n    python System\\Launchers\\launch.py\n) else (\n    where py >nul 2>nul\n    if %errorlevel%==0 (\n        py System\\Launchers\\launch.py\n    ) else (\n        echo Python was not found.\n        pause\n    )\n)\n",
